contentrichtext.text: '''TZ''' or '''tz''' may refer to: * [[The Twilight Zone]] * [[Tappan Zee Bridge]] * [[Tappan Zee High School]], a public high school in Orangeburg, New York, United States * [[time zone]] * [[Sony_VAIO#Current_models|Sony Vaio TZ]] * [[tz database]] * the IATA code for [[Scoot]] * the IATA code for [[ATA Airlines]] * TZ, The chemical weapon designation of the United States military for [[saxitoxin]], a bacterial sodium channel blocker * [[Tanzania]], ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code ** [[.tz]], the country code top level domain (ccTLD) for Tanzania * [[Transformation Zone]], a term used in cervical cancer therapy, the area of the cervix where dysplasia and abnormal cell growth occur * [[tz (newspaper)]], a German tabloid newspaper from Munich {{disambiguation}}
